			  </div>
			  <video controls autoplay loop preload="auto" title="你被骗了" class="yt-video relative mx-auto mt-12 w-full max-w-4xl rounded-3xl border border-gray-300 shadow-2xl dark:border-gray-700 lg:mt-20"><source src="https://file.dragonjay.top/api/raw/?path=/video/nibeipianla.mp4" type="video/mp4" /></video>
